/span>中有广泛</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yfb ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">叙述，大家可以去参阅。 </div><div class="t m0 x1e h4 y214 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls49 ws0">3、破有无生因：是抉择万法的“果”无自性。其观察</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 ybe ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls22 ws0">方法是“有法不应生，无亦不应生”<span class="_ _a"></span><span class="ls3a">，也就是说，果若在因</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 ybf ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">位时存在，<span class="_ _f"></span>就不必再生，<span class="_ _f"></span>因为已有之故；<span class="_ _f"></span>果若在因位时无有，</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yc0 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">则永远不能生，<span class="_ _8"></span>犹如石女的儿子。<span class="_ _d"></span>这种推理，<span class="_ _8"></span>在<span class="_ _d"></span>《中观根本</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 yc1 ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">慧论》中讲得比较多。 </div><div class="t m0 x1e h4 yfd ffa fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4、<span class="_ _d"></span>破四句生因：<span class="_ _d"></span>是同时观察<span class="_ _d"></span>“因”<span class="_ _d"></span>与<span class="_ _d"></span>“果”<span class="_ _a"></span>，<span class="_ _d"></span>在<span class="_ _d"></span>《中观</div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
